cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI 

The paper discusses the use of artificial intelligence and machine learning tools for character recognition of handwritten documents, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of natural language processing techniques (cs.CL) and deep learning algorithms (cs.LG, cs.AI) for OCR. Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
